<HEAD>
    <TITLE></TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<IMG SRC="norway.gif" ALIGN="right" VSPACE =5 HSPACE=10  NATURALSIZEFLAG=
"3"> <BR>
<H2><br><br>THE NORWEGIAN NOBEL COMMITTEE</H2>
<br><br><br>
<P>
<h3 align="center">The Nobel Peace Prize for 1987</h3>
<P><br>
<A HREF="http://www.nobel.no/indexen.html">The Norwegian Nobel 
Committee</A> has decided
to award the 1987 Nobel Peace Prize to President <B>Oscar Arias Sanchez</B>
of Costa Rica, for his work for peace in Central America, efforts which
led to the accord signed in Guatemala on August 7 this year. <BR>
<BR>
As the main architect of the peace plan, President Arias made an outstanding
contribution to the possible return of stability and peace to a region long
torn by strife and civil war. He thereby carried on the constructive work
begun by the Contadora group. <BR>
<BR>
The Committee attaches importance to the fact that the accord is the result
of responsible cooperation between the five signatory states. As such, it
lays solid foundations for the further development of democracy and for
open cooperation between peoples and states. <BR>
<BR>
A prerequisite for lasting peace is the realization of democratic ideals,
with freedom and equality for all. In the opinion of the Committee, Oscar
Arias is a strong spokesman for those ideals. The importance of his work
for peace will extend beyond Central America. <BR>
