<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Nobel Institute for Neurophysiology - Annual Report for
1994</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY>
<H1>Nobel Institute for Neurophysiology</H1>
<BR><BR>
<H3>Annual Report for 1994</H3>
<BR><H4>During 1994 the research staff of the Neurophysiology division has
consisted of:</H4>
<PRE>
Professor 		Sten Grillner		director

Professor emeritus 	Curt von Euler
Professor emeritus 	Bernard Frankenhaeuser


