Professor 		Grigori Orlovski	research position at MFR
Docent			Lennart Brodin		research associate
Docent 			Peter Wall&eacute;n		lecturer in Neurophysiology
Docent 			Peter &Aring;rhem		lecturer in Physiology/Neurophysiology
Docent 			Hans Forssberg		lecturer in Clin.Neurosci./dept Pediatrics
