<DOCNO>WT05-B11-58</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA061-000342-B022-396</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.nobel.se:80/illpres/medicine-1996/implications.html 130.237.132.126 19970115110635 text/html 5234
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Enterprise/2.0c
Date: Wed, 15 Jan 1997 11:08:44 GMT
