<BODY>

<H1><FONT SIZE=10><CITE>

<IMG SRC="art/melogo.GIF" ALIGN=baseline WIDTH=253 HEIGHT=68 ALT="Mining
Engineering">
</CITE> Advertiser Profiles</FONT></H1>

<P><CITE><FONT SIZE=5>A Resource of Services and Products</FONT><HR></FONT>
</CITE></P>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~pubs/navigator.html"><IMG SRC="art/navbtn.GIF" BORDER=0></A></P></CENTER>

<BR CLEAR=all>

<DL>

<!-- Main text here -->
<H2>
<HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=left>
<A HREF="http://www.ittacpump.com">ITT A-C Pump</A>
</H2>
<P>1150 Tennessee Avenue<BR>
Cincinnati, OH, 45229</P>

<! -- Description of ITT A-C Pump -->
<P>ITT A-C Pump produces the widest range of pumps for mining and the mineral processing industry of any manufacturer in the world; elastomer-lined and hard metal slurry pumps, ANSI process pumps, magnetic drive pumps, water supply and wastewater treatment pumps and complete fire pump systems.

<P>For more information about ITT A-C Pump products and services, call 1-800-734-PUMP or visit our <A HREF="http://www.ittacpump.com"><B>website</B></A>.
<! -- end description of this company -->

<H2>
<HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=left>
<A HREF="http://www.maptek.com">MAPTEK/KRJA Systems, Inc.</A>
</H2>
<P>165 Sout Union Blvd., Ste. 777<BR>
Lakewood, CO, 80228</P>

<! -- Description of MAPTEK/KRJA Systems, Inc. -->
<P>MAPTEK is the leading developer of 3-D geological modeling, mapping and mine planning software, in use at over 200 locations worldwide. MAPTEK's VULCAN software covers all aspects of mining, from geologic modeling to design, resource estimation and restoration. VULCAN interactive graphics software encompasses both coal and hard rock mining.

<P>For more information about MAPTEK/KRJA Systems, Inc. products and services, call 303-763-4919, e-mail <A HREF="mailto:info@maptek.com">info@maptek.com</A> or visit our <A HREF="http://www.maptek.com"><B>website</B></A>.
<! -- end description of this company -->

<H2>
<HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=left>
Ramsey - A Thermo Sentron Company</H2>
<P>501 90th Avenue NW<BR>
Minneapolis, MN, 55433</P>

<! -- Description of Ramsey -->
<P>Ramsey manufactures weighing, control and monitoring products for a broad variety of industrial requirements. The company's primary technological strength is in dynamic weighing devices including belt conveyor scales, weighing feeders and in-line automatic weighing equipment for packaged goods. Other products include metal detection, coal and mineral sampling systems, level controls and a veriety of specialty control products. Ramsey companies are located in six European countries, Canada, mexico, Australia and South Africa, and is headquartered in Minneapolis.

<P>For more information about Ramsey products and services, call 612-873-2500, fax 612-783-2525 (attention: Don Bina).
<! -- end description of this company -->

<H2>
<HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=left>
<A HREF="http://www.sprung.com">Sprung Instant Structures, Inc.</A>
</H2>
<P>1001 10th Avenue SW<BR>
Calgary, Alberta, T2R 0B7, Canada</P>

<! -- Description of Sprung Instant Structures, Inc. -->
<P>New Building Technology

<P>

<P>We are manufacturers of stressed membrane structures extensively utilized by the mining industry for all applications from bulk ore storage, ore processing, vehicle maintenance, tank enclosures, copper concentrate storage to on-site dining and recreation facilities. Delivered from inventory, erection can be completed in a fraction of the time and cost of conventional construction. By design the structures shed snow and can be designed to withstand extreme high winds. Lease or purchase.

<P>For more information about Sprung Instant Structures, Inc. products and services, call 1-800-528-9899 or 1-800-661-1163 in Canada, fax 403-229-1980 or visit our <A HREF="http://www.sprung.com"><B>website</B></A>.
<! -- end description of this company -->

</DL>

