<TITLE>SME Membership Benefits</TITLE>

<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:pubs@rmii.com">

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<H1><FONT SIZE=10>

<A HREF="index.html">
<IMG SRC="art/smelogo.GIF" ALIGN=left HSPACE=12 BORDER=0></A>

SME Membership</FONT>

</H1>

<P><CITE><FONT SIZE=5>Benefits of SME Membership</FONT><HR></FONT>

</CITE></P>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~pubs/navigator.html"><IMG SRC="art/navbtn.GIF" BORDER=0></A></P></CENTER>

<BR CLEAR=all>

<!-- Document Body Text -->

<DT><H3>MEMBERSHIP BENEFITS INFORMATION</H3>

<DT><B>Insurance</B>

<DD>US SME members participate with other engineering society members to enjoy group rates on health, accident, life, medicare supplement, disability income and cancer expense insurance.  Some health, accident and life insurance is available to US residents traveling or working abroad on a short-term basis.   Professional Liability Insurance is also available to SME members within the United States.   Call 1-800-763-3132 for information on how to contact the providers of these services.

<DT><B>Car Rental</B>

<DD>SME members within the United States enjoy discount rates with both Hertz and Avis car rental companies.

<DT><B>JobBANK USA</B>

<DD>A nationwide electronic resume service is available at discount rates to SME members.  JobBank USA serves the full spectrum of employment opportunities.

<DT><B>Credit Card</B>

<DD>A  Mastercard is available through the society with the option of higher level credit limits.

<DT><B><A HREF='http://www.asaenet.org/mellon'>Mellon</A> Mortgage Program</B>

<DD>For home purchase or refinancing, Mellon has innovative programs for buyers and sellers.

</DL>

<P><HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=left> Please feel free to <A HREF="mailto:pubs@rmii.com">report any problems</A> encountered on this page.</P>

<P>If you have specific questions about any items here, please contact <A HREF="mailto:smenet@aol.com">SME</A>. <STRONG>Please be certain to address correspondence to Customer Service</STRONG>.

