<!-- Document Body Text --> <DL>

<DL>

<DT><H3>Students in SME</H3>

<DD>Student members are the future of SME.  Student members have opportunities to network with peers and professionals within the society and begin to establish a standing in the industry.  Student Chapters provide a link between the school and industry which allows students to engage in activities necessary for professional development.

<UL>

<LI><B><A HREF="benefits_student.stml">Benefits of Student Membership</A></B><BR>

Students receive substantial discounts on meetings and books, among many other benefits of SME membership. 

<LI><B><A HREF="student_finance.stml">Student-Related Financial Policies</A></B>

<LI><B><A HREF="how_student.stml">How to Become a Student Member of SME</A></B>

</UL>

<DT><H3>Student Contests</H3>

<DD>Plan to enter the SME Outstanding Student contests.  Win $500 and expenses toward a trip to the next SME Annual Meeting!  Deadline:  December 1.

<UL>

<LI>Contest Guidelines

<UL>

<LI><B><A HREF="student_papers.stml">Outstanding Student Paper Contests</A></B>

<LI><B><A HREF="student_chapters.stml">Outstanding Student Chapter Contest</A></B>

</UL>

</UL>

<DT><H3>Meetings and Activities</H3>

<UL>

<LI><B><A HREF="mtgcalendar.stml">SME Meetings</A></B><BR>

SME meetings provide students an opportunity to meet industry professionals, attend technical sessions and short courses.  Join us for the next SME meeting!

<LI><B><A HREF="world_notes.stml">Notes from Around the World</A></B><BR>

SME students are active in many different areas.  Click for information on some recent activities.

<LI><B><A HREF="student_tips.stml">Tips for Student Activities</A></B><BR>

These tips for activities come from SME Student Chapters, but you can get involved in your local minerals community and your own professional development even before you become a member.

</UL>

<DT><H3><A HREF="student_chaps.stml">Student Chapters</A></H3>

<UL>

<LI><B><A HREF="make_chapter.stml">How to Form an SME Student Chapter</A></B>

