<HEAD>

<TITLE>SME Students: Accreditation.</TITLE>

<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:pubs@rmii.com">

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<H1><FONT SIZE=10>

<A HREF="membership.stml">
<IMG SRC="art/campus.GIF" ALIGN=right HSPACE=12 BORDER=0></A>

<A HREF="index.html">
<IMG SRC="art/smelogo.GIF" ALIGN=left HSPACE=12 BORDER=0></A>

SME Students</FONT>

</H1>

<P><CITE><FONT SIZE=5>Accreditation</FONT><HR></FONT>

</CITE></P>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~pubs/navigator.html"><IMG SRC="art/navbtn.GIF" BORDER=0></A></P></CENTER>

<BR CLEAR=all>

<!-- Document Body Text --> <DL>

<DL>

<DT><H3>Accreditation of Engineering Programs at Colleges and Universities</H3>

<DD>The <B><A HREF="http://www.abet.ba.md.us" TARGET="_top">Accreditation Board for Engineering and Technology (ABET)</A></B> accredits engineering programs in the United States.  It is supported by its participating bodies and the accredited programs.  SME is one of the 21 participating bodies of ABET, and is represented on ABET's Board of Directors and Accreditation Commissions.

<P><A HREF="about_accreditation.stml">About Accreditation</A>

<UL>

<LI>Accreditation in the United States

<LI>International Accreditation

<LI>SME's Role in Accreditation

<UL>

<LI>Participation and Representation

<LI>Criteria (<A HREF="mincrit.stml">Mining</A> and <A HREF="geprog.stml">Geology</A>)

</UL>

</UL></P>

<P><A HREF="support_accreditation.stml">Support the Accreditation Process</A></P>

<UL>

<LI>How You Can Support the Accreditation Process

<LI>Current ABET Issues

<LI>Accreditation and Curricular Issues Committee

<LI>Council of Education

</UL></P>

<P><A HREF="program_eval.stml">Program Evaluators</A>

