<TITLE>Membership: Benefits of Student Membership</TITLE>

<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:pubs@rmii.com">

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<H1><FONT SIZE=10>

<A HREF="membership.stml">
<IMG SRC="art/campus.GIF" ALIGN=right HSPACE=12 BORDER=0></A>

<A HREF="index.html">
<IMG SRC="art/smelogo.GIF" ALIGN=left HSPACE=12 BORDER=0></A>

Membership</FONT>

</H1>

<P><CITE><FONT SIZE=5>Benefits of Student Membership</FONT><HR></FONT>

</CITE></P>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~pubs/navigator.html"><IMG SRC="art/navbtn.GIF" BORDER=0></A></P></CENTER>

<BR CLEAR=all>

<!-- Document Body Text --> <DL>

<DL>

<DT><H3>Association</H3><DD>Broaden your knowledge, develop leadership qualities and strengthen social bonds through participation in SME activities in association with fellow students and professionals.

<DT><H3><A HREF="mtgcalendar.stml">Meetings</A></H3><DD>Student Members have the opportunity to attend local, regional and national meetings of the society, usually at student rates.

<DT><H3><A HREF="publications.stml">Publications</A></H3><DD>Student Members receive <I><A HREF="me.stml">Mining Engineering,</A></I> the official journal of the society, and are eligible for discounts on books and publications of other AIME-member societies.  On graduation and advancement to Associate Member status, Student Members receive their choice of a book published by the Seeley W. Mudd Fund as a gift.

<DT><H3>Directory</H3><DD>Student Members appear in SME's directory of members, published annually in the <I>SME Resource Guide.</I>

<DT><H3>Awards</H3><DD>Student Members are eligible to compete in the <B><A HREF="student_papers.stml">SME Outstanding Student Paper Contests</A></B>.  Student Members may apply for SME division-sponsored scholarship awards.

<DT><H3>Free Ads</H3><DD>Student Members may place two free 36-word advertisements per year in the Employment Service "Positions Wanted" column in <I>Mining Engineering</I> (see the Employment Service page in <I>Mining Engineering</I> for guidelines).

<P>Student Membership in SME is only $15 per year.  Find out <<B>A HREF="how_student.stml">how to become a Student Member</A></B>.</P>

</DL>

