<H1>1998 CALL FOR PAPERS</H1></TH></TR>

<TR><TD><IMG SRC="orlando.GIF" ALIGN=left WIDTH=200 HEIGHT=84></TD>

<TD ROWSPAN=2><IMG SRC="newGlobe.GIF" ALIGN=right WIDTH=270 HEIGHT=265></TD></TR>

<TR><TD VALIGN="bottom"><FONT FACE="Helvetica,Arial">

<B>LOOK FOR NEW AND TIMELY PROGRAMS INCLUDING:</B></FONT>

<P>Bulk Material Handling</P>

<P>Environmental Division<BR>(<FONT COLOR="#000088">first program year!</FONT>)</P>

<P>Latin American Perspectives Symposium</P>

</TD></TR></TABLE>

<TABLE BGCOLOR="#aaffff" WIDTH=35% ALIGN=left CELLSPACING=0 CELLPADDING=6 ALIGN=left>

<TR><TD><FONT FACE="Helvetica,Arial">

The Program Committee for the 1998 SME Annual Meeting and Exhibit has issued the following Call for Papers.

<P>HOW TO

<UL>

	<LI>Send a preliminary abstract for consideration to the chair listed for that session.

	<LI>Abstract should include:

		<UL>

			<LI>Title

			<LI>Authors and their affiliations

			<LI>100 word abstract

		</UL>

	<LI>If you submit the same abstract for multiple sessions, please advise all chairs to avoid duplication within the program.

	<LI>Deadline: February 1, 1997

</UL>

<P>Session chairs will advise authors of acceptance or otherwise no later than May, 1997. Following acceptance, SME will mail Authors' Kits to the primary author for each accepted paper.

</FONT></TD></TR>

<TR><TD BGCOLOR="#ffffff">

<FONT FACE="Helvetica,Arial">

<CENTER>

Should your paper be accepted <BR>

the following deadlines apply:

<TABLE>

<TR><TH>Final Abstracts</TH><TH>August 1, 1997</TH></TR>

<TR><TH>Manuscripts</TH><TH>November 1, 1997</TH></TR>

</TABLE>

(Manuscripts for symposia proceedings are due earlier).

</CENTER></FONT></TD></TR>

