<HEAD>

<TITLE>Publications: Overview</TITLE>

<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:pubs@rmii.com">

</HEAD>

<BODY>

<H1><FONT SIZE=10>

<A HREF="index.html">
<IMG SRC="art/smelogo.GIF" ALIGN=left HSPACE=12 BORDER=0></A>

<IMG SRC="art/publogo.GIF" ALIGN=right HSPACE=12>

Publications</FONT>

</H1>

<P><CITE><FONT SIZE=5>Overview</FONT><HR></FONT>

</CITE></P>

<P><CENTER><A HREF="http://rainbow.rmii.com/~pubs/navigator.html"><IMG SRC="art/navbtn.GIF" BORDER=0></A></P></CENTER>

<BR CLEAR=all>

<!-- Document Body Text -->

<P>SME is mandated to produce publications of the highest quality to serve professionals working in the minerals industry.

<P>SME's flagship publication is <CITE><B><A HREF="me.stml"><I>Mining Engineering</I></A></B></CITE>, its official monthly magazine. <CITE><I>Mining Engineering</I></CITE> features news and topical articles about the international industry and also contains peer-reviewed technical papers.

<P>SME's quarterly research journal is <CITE><A HREF="mmpj.stml"><B><I>Minerals and Metallurgical Processing</I></B></A></CITE>. It covers the processing of metallic, nonmetallic and fuel ores. All papers in <CITE>Minerals and Metallurgical Processing</CITE> are peer-reviewed.

<P>An annual <CITE>Transactions</CITE> volume is also published by SME in print and CD-ROM form. This bound volume contains the peer-reviewed papers that appear in <CITE>Mining Engineering</CITE>, <CITE>Minerals and Metallurgical Processing</CITE> and more than two dozen additional peer-reviewed papers that are published only in this archival volume.

<P><A HREF="preprints.stml"><B>Preprints</B></A> are published of all SME annual meeting papers received prior to the meeting. These preprints are available for sale at the annual meeting and afterward.

<P>SME publishes conference proceedings, handbooks, textbooks, CD-ROMs, monographs and other books. A list of SME publications describes books by author and title; all of which are available for purchase.

<P><HR WIDTH=50% ALIGN=left> Please feel free to <A HREF="mailto:smenet@aol.com">report any problems</A> encountered on this page.</P>

<P>If you have specific questions about any items here, please contact <A HREF="mailto:smenet@aol.com">SME</A>. <STRONG>Please be certain to address correspondence to Customer Service</STRONG>.

