<H1>
<A HREF="bldgphoto.stml">
<IMG SRC="art/bldg.jpg" ALIGN=right height=89 width=172 vspace=0 hspace=5 BORDER=0></A>
<IMG SRC="art/smebug.GIF"></H1>

<!-- Document Body Text -->

<TABLE>
<A NAME="sme">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="top"><P><A HREF="sme.stml"><IMG SRC="art/smelogo.GIF" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></P>
<TD><H2><A HREF="sme.stml">SME - Who We Are</A></H2>
<P><I>
The Society for Mining, Metallurgy and Exploration, Inc. a member society of 
<A HREF="aime.stml">AIME</A> - is an international, nonprofit association 
of some 17,000 professionals working in the mineral industries. SME members have 
the technical expertise acquired through training and experience and the innovative 
ability to enhance their industry.
<UL>
<LI><A HREF="espanol.stml">Informaci&oacute;n general (en espa&ntilde;ol)</A>
</UL>
</P></I>
</TR></A>

<A NAME="new">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="top"><P><A HREF="new.stml">
<IMG SRC="art/newlogo.GIF" ALIGN=left BORDER=0 height=63 width=70></A></P>
<TD><H2><A HREF="new.stml">What's New</A></H2>
<P><I>
SME offers hundreds of <A HREF="books/booklist.stml">books</A> and technical reports, 
<A HREF="meads.stml">product/service information</A> and several 
information-packed periodicals, provides the opportunities for industry professionals 
to <A HREF="mtgindex.stml">meet</A> and share knowledge and operational experiences, 
stimulates science education and offers colorful items of industry 
<A HREF="memorabilia/index.html">memorabilia</A>.</P>

<P><FONT FACE="Helvetica,Arial" COLOR="#008737">
<B>NEW - <A HREF="mtg/" TARGET="_top">1997 Annual Meeting Materials</A></B></FONT> are now online...</P>

<P><FONT FACE="Helvetica,Arial" COLOR="#008737">
<B>NEW - <A HREF="mtg/exhibitors.html" TARGET="_top">1997 ShowGuide</A></B></FONT> now available online...</P>

</I></TR></A>

<A NAME="mem">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="top"><P><A HREF="members.stml">
<IMG SRC="art/memlogo.GIF" ALIGN=left BORDER=0 width=65 height=66></A></P>
<TD><H2><A HREF="members.stml">Membership</A></H2>
<P><I>
Members are the life blood of SME. Its many divisions and committees offer 
professionals an opportunity to advance in their industry and have a say in the future 
direction of the worldwide minerals and mining enterprises.
</I></P>
<P><UL>
<LI>Membership <A HREF="benefits.stml">Benefits</A> and Services
<LI>How to <A HREF="joinchange.stml">Join or Change Your Membership</A>
</UL>
</P></TR></A>

<A NAME="campus">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="top"><H2><A HREF="students.stml"><IMG SRC="art/campus.GIF" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></H2>
<TD><H2><A HREF="careers.stml">SME Students</A></H2>
<I>SME's mission is to advance the worldwide mining and minerals community through 
information exchange and professional development. Toward this purpose, SME is actively 
involved in accrediting minerals-related programs at colleges and universities across 
the United States. SME student members represent the future of minerals engineering. SME provides many benefits to the student member, including 
scholarships available from SMEs divisions.
</I></P>
<P>Information about:<UL>
<LI><A HREF="accreditation.stml">Accreditation</A>;
<LI><A HREF="students.stml">Student Memberships</A> and its 
<A HREF="benefits_student.stml">benefits</A>; and
<LI><A HREF="scholarships.stml">Scholarships</A>.
</UL></P></TR></A>

<A NAME="careers">
<TR>
<TD VALIGN="top"><H2><A HREF="careers.stml"><IMG SRC="art/careers.GIF" ALIGN=left BORDER=0></A></H2>
