<H1><FONT SIZE=7><IMG SRC="art/meetlogo.GIF" ALIGN=left>
1997 SME Annual Meeting and Exhibit</FONT></H1>
<H2><FONT SIZE=6>Exhibitor Prospectus</FONT></H2>


<BR CLEAR=all>

<CENTER><H1>SME Exhibitors speak for themselves</H1></CENTER>
<H2>Magotteaux International</H2>
<H3>Greg Weller<BR>
Northwest Sales Engineer</H3>
<P><CITE>"With today's shrinking budgets, we are forced to utilize every advertising dollar at its maximum effectiveness. The SME Annual Meeting and Exhibit provides a venue for assembling our key contacts in the plants, managers, corporate staff and other decision-makers who are vital to our long-term customer relationships. The SME Show allows us to disseminate more ideas to a broader segment of the international mining community than at any other time of the year." </CITE></P>

<H2>Mine Development Associates</H2>
<H3>Neil Prenn<BR>
President</H3>
<P><CITE>"The SME Annual Meeting and Exhibit is the most important mining industry exhibit for us. We see the people we need to reach: operations personnel, corporate executives, explorationists, and other service companies. Attendees are active in the industry and receptive to seeing what's new. The meeting allows us to keep up on industry practices and issues. We haven't missed a show in quite a while and don't expect to miss any coming up."</CITE></P>

<H2>Cubex Limited</H2>
<H3>Jim Peterson<BR>
International Area Manager</H3>
<P><CITE>"Cubex Limited participates in many trade shows. This past year we displayed for the first time a piece of heavy equipment at the SME Exhibit. We have never had better support and help in setting up a heavy equipment display. The can do attitude and assistance we received from SME staff helped us to have a very successful event. The quality of attendees has made our investment pay off. See us again next year!"</CITE></P>

<H2>Outokumpu Mintec U.S.A. Inc.</H2>
<H3>Terry Braden<BR>
Manager, Analyzer and Automation Division</H3>
<P><CITE>"Outokumpu has been involved in the U.S. mining industry and SME for more than 15 years. One common factor has been the high quality and value of the SME Annual Meeting and Exhibit. Every meeting we have attended has offered opportunities to meet new potential customers and renew old friendships. It has offered a forum for us to introduce our new technologies and solidify our position with our old technologies. We look forward to another 15 years with SME." </CITE></P>

