<CENTER><H1>The Mechanics of Exhibiting</H1></CENTER>

<H2>Booth Reservations</H2>

<H3>Returning Exhibitors</H3>

<P>Exhibit space for the 1997 SME Exhibit will be selected on the basis of earned priority points. Priority points for exhibiting companies are determined by exhibit history, booth size, advertising and sponsorship in past years' SME Exhibits. 1996 SME Exhibitors had the opportunity to select booth space for the 1997 Exhibit on March 13, 1996 during priority space selection meetings. Booths could not be reserved before March 13, 1996.</P>

<H3>New Exhibitors</H3>

<P>If you did not reserve a booth on March 13 at the priority space meeting, please review the floor plan and complete the enclosed Exhibitor Contract indicating your preferred booth locations.</P>

<H3>Prior to October 31, 1996</H3>

<P>Contracts must be accompanied by a $650 per booth deposit.</P>

<H3>After October 31, 1996</H3>

<P>Contracts must be accompanied by full payment.</P>

<H3>Deposits should be made payable to SME and mailed to:</H3>

<P>SME Meetings Dept., Attn: Exhibit Coordinator, PO Box 625002, Littleton, CO 80162-5002, Phone (303) 973-9550 ext. 213, 800-763-3132, Fax (303) 979-3461</P>

<H2>Premium Booth Space</H2>

<P>Shown shaded on the floor plan. <STRONG>Shading does not indicate reserved booth space.</STRONG></P>

<H2>Space Costs</H2>

<P><UL>
<LI>$1200 for standard 10' x 10' booth
<LI>$1300 for premium 10' x 10' booth (shown shaded on floor plan)
<LI>$1350 for 10' x 10' booth in Mining Software Pavilion (indicated on floor plan)
</UL></P>

<H2>Booth Rental Includes</H2>

<P><UL>
<LI>7" x 44" booth sign with company name, city, state and booth number.
<LI>8' back drape with 3' draped side rails.
<LI>General security.
<LI>2 complimentary Full Meeting Registrations for each 10' x 10' booth valid for technical session attendance and exhibit hall entrance.
<LI>4 Exhibit Only registrations for each 10' x 10' booth for exhibit hall entrance.
</UL></P>

