<H2><FONT FACE='Geneva,Arial'>ACKNOWLEDGMENTS</FONT></H2>

<P>Several events of the meeting will be supported by many generous corporate sponsors. All contributing firms receive a sponsorship ribbon for their staff as recognition of their support. All contributors will be acknowledged in the Annual Meeting pocket program and in the 1997 Sponsors Booklet. For further information, contact Joette Cross, SME Meetings Manager, at (303) 973-9550.</P>

