<FONT FACE="Helvetica,Arial">
<H3><I><BR CLEAR=left>
Business Strategies in Global Mining 
</I></FONT><BR>

Tuesday, February 25, 2:00 PM, A109/111

</H3></FONT>
</TH></TR></FONT></TABLE>


