<h2 align=center><b>Hot List of Links to Advertising Law-Related 
Sites</b></h2>
<h3 align=center><b>Key Federal Agencies and Other Federal Resources</b></h3>
<p>Here's a listing of key federal agencies and other federal resources where 
additional information on advertising law may be found.</p>
<h4><img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://law.house.gov/cfr.htm">Code of Federal Regulations</a><br>
