<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.access.gpo.gov/su_docs">Federal Register</a><br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.fcc.gov/">Federal Communications Commission</a><br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.ftc.gov">Federal Trade Commission </a><br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.fda.gov">Food and Drug Administration </a><br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.fdli.org/welcome.html">Food and Drug Law Institute</a><br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.access.gpo.gov/su_docs/gils/gils.html">Government Information Locator Service</a><br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://lcweb.loc.gov">Library of Congress</a> <br>
<img src="blue-b~2.gif" align=bottom width=12 height=12> <a href="http://www.fie.com/www/us_gov.htm">List of Federal Government WWW Servers</a><br>
