<HEAD>


<title>Advertising Law-Related News Briefs for September 1996</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="description" content="The following news briefs examine 
advertising law-related actions during the month of September 1996.">
<meta name="keywords" content="law, advertising, advertising law, advertising 
