<p align=center><font size=5><b>Brand-New Supplementary Index for<br>
Advertising Compliance Service</b></font></center><br>

<p>This <b>Supplementary Index </b>covers the period January 1996--July 1996. It supplements 
the Main Index that covers the three-year period 1993-1995. References are to Tab#, Article# and Page#. For example, the 
entry, &quot;AAF, 2:271.1&quot; can be found at Tab #2, Article #271, Page 1. </p>

<p align=center><font size=4><strong>INDEX to VOLUME XVI<br>
BULLETINS #345--358<br>
ISSUES #1--14<br>
JANUARY 1996--JULY 1996</strong></font></center><br>

