12:34.2. </p>
<p>Johnson &amp; Johnson v. GAC Int'l, Inc., 862 F.2d 975 (2d Cir. 1988), 2:268.7; 
17:41.2. </p>
<p>Johnson &amp; Johnson-Merck Consumer Pharmaceuticals Co. v. SmithKline 
Beecham Cop., 960 F.2d 294, 297-98 (2d Cir. 1992), 2:268.7; 17:41.3. </p>
<p>Kovacs v. Cooper, 336 U.S. 77, 89 (1949), 18:28.2. </p>
<p>Kulbushan Karbal and Noesys, Inc. v. IDD Enterprises, L.P., and Martin v. 
McCarthy, 95 Civ. 1161 (DAB), United States District Court for the Southern 
District of New York, 1996 U.S. Dist. LEXIS 1127, February 5, 1996, 2:268.5. </p>
