<p>Skil Corp. v. Rockwell Int'l Corp., 375 F.Supp. 777, 782-83 (E.D. Ill. 1974), 
2:268.7; 17:41.2. </p>
<p>Smithkline Beecham Consumer Healthcare, L.P. v. Johnson &amp; Johnson-Merck 
