<title>Advertising Law: Tobacco Advertising; Children and Tobacco, Executive Summary, Final Rule</title>
<meta name="description" content="Advertising Law: Tobacco Advertising; 
Children and Tobacco, Executive Summary, Final Rule.">
<meta name="keywords" content="advertising law, law, advertising, 
advertising law, advertising law, tobacco, tobacco, tobacco, tobacco, 
tobacco, tobacco, tobacco, nicotine, nicotine, nicotine, nicotine, nicotine, 
nicotine, nicotine, cigarettes, cigarettes, cigarettes, cigarettes, cigarettes, 
cigarettes, cigarettes, FDA, advertising law, FDA, FDA, FDA, advertising law, 
