<P>
<UL>
Here's the <B>scoop</B> on what's new with <A HREF="../meet/meet.html">InterVU</A> as of December 9, 1996.<BR>
<BR>
<H2>Announcing the InterVU Network</H2>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
The InterVU Network enables Content Providers to offer high quality video, high speed video delivery and improved Web site performance. Learn more about this exciting new service in the <A HREF="../service/service.html">Video Network Services</A> section of our Web site.    
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<H2>Announcing the InterVU Network Enabled Player</H2>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<A HREF="../player/player.html">Version 2.0 of the InterVU Network Enabled Player for Windows 95 and Windows NT is now available.</A>  The InterVU Player 2.0 automatically retrieves video files from the InterVU Network in order to speed their delivery to your PC. The SmartVU&#153; Network Optimizer which is included in the InterVU Player 2.0, chooses from among the video servers on the InterVU Network the server with the fastest electronic communication route to your PC.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<H2>Other News:</H2>
<H3>Look for the <A HREF="../partners/menu.html">InterVU Video Guide:</A></H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
 Preview movies and shows airing each month on the <U>Lifetime</U> channel on their Web site. If you like cars, boats, planes, and motorcycles, buckle up, hold on tight and check out <U>Speedvision</U>'s Web site. See the future of video on the Internet with Yachting<I>net</I>, a Times Mirror site for <U>Yachting Magazine</U>.  
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<BR>
<H3>InterVU Player latest versions:</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
<A HREF="../player/player.html">Download the </A>October 25, version 0.96, release for the Macintosh PowerPC and 68K.

<BR><BR>
<A HREF="../player/player.html">Download the</A> December 9, version 2.0, release for Windows 95 or Windows NT.</A>
</BLOCKQUOTE>
</UL>
</P>
