InterVU Network Sales
</FONT></CENTER>
<BR CLEAR=LEFT><IMG SRC="images/bluebarsm.gif" ALIGN=LEFT><BR></P>
<BR>
<UL>
<UL>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B><FONT COLOR="#DC143C">
Customer Service
</FONT></B></FONT>
<P>
Our highly trained personnel and our strategic partners are available to assist you in all stages of delivering high quality interactive Web video.  Simply provide us your video in any format and InterVU handles the rest -- no expensive hardware to purchase, no need to purchase extra bandwidth capacity, and no special video Internet knowledge.  Once you elect to use the InterVU Network, integrating video into your Web pages is as simple as adding a single standard "embed" statement to your HTML Web page(s).  The InterVU Control Center keeps track of video delivery performance 24 hours a day, 7 days a week and provides you with monthly activity and performance reports.
</P>
<P>
Have Web development or video needs?  InterVU has partnered with leading Web and video production companies to assist you with all your Web development and video production requirements.
</P>
<P>
InterVU, your complete source for high quality, cost-effective Internet video services.
</P>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B><FONT COLOR="#DC143C">
Pricing
</FONT></B></FONT>
<P>
Get the InterVU Network cost-performance advantage:
<BR>
<BR>
<UL>
<LI TYPE=CIRCLE>
No - Expensive proprietary servers to purchase.
<LI>
No - Costly Internet bandwidth connections.
<LI>
No - Server or client software to purchase.
<LI>
No - Simultaneous viewer connection charges.
<LI>
No - Single site trying to serve the world.
<BR>
<BR>
<LI TYPE=DISC>
<B>Yes - Pay only for high quality, high speed video delivered to your viewers.</B>
</UL>
<P>
For more information on service pricing contact your InterVU sales representative at <A HREF="mailto:sales@intervu.com">sales@intervu.com</A> or (619) 350-1600.
</P>
<BR>
<FONT SIZE=+2><B><FONT COLOR="#DC143C">
Get the <A HREF="service/service.html">InterVU Network</A> <A HREF="service/advantage.html">Advantage!</A>
</FONT></B></FONT>
<P>
To initiate your video delivery service or to receive a presentation on the InterVU Network contact your InterVU sales representative at <A HREF="mailto:sales@intervu.com">sales@intervu.com</A> or at  <B>(619) 350-1600.</B>
</P>
</UL>
</UL>
