<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+5>

End-to-End Video Solutions

</FONT></CENTER>
<BR CLEAR=LEFT><IMG SRC="../images/bluebarsm.gif" ALIGN=LEFT><BR></P>
<BR>
<UL>


<P>
The bar is quickly being raised in bringing and keeping the mass market audience visiting your Internet site(s).  In the coming months, Content Providers will increasingly strive to integrate audio and video communications into their content offerings.  In doing so, there will be many tradeoffs to consider - video/audio formats, quality of compression, streaming, access speeds, software requirements, costs, interoperability and so on.
</P>
<P>InterVU is here to help you cut through the complexities and support you in creating and delivering the best video enriched Web pages for your site - cost effectively.  <A HREF="../order.html">Contact us</A> about a full-service Internet video solution or any of the specific services itemized below.</P>
</UL>
