<HEAD>
<TITLE>
About InterVU Inc.
</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF", TEXT="#000000", LTEXT="#0000CD", VLINK="#008000", ALINK="#DC143C">
<P>
<A HREF="../index.html"><IMG BORDER=0 ALT=InterVU Logo SRC="../images/intlogosm.gif" ALIGN=LEFT></A>
<BR><CENTER><FONT SIZE=+5>
The Company
</FONT></CENTER>
<BR CLEAR=LEFT><IMG SRC="../images/bluebarsm.gif" ALIGN=LEFT><BR></P>
<UL>
<P>
<BR>
<H3>InterVU's Mission</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
Our mission is to be the leader in providing high speed, high quality, cost-effective video delivery services for the Internet.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
<H3>InterVU's Position Statement</H3>
<BLOCKQUOTE>
The InterVU Network is for Content Providers and Website developers who want to provide the highest quality video messages on the Internet.  The InterVU Network uses Smart Mirror&#153; Technology to deliver on-demand video content to viewers at the fastest speed.  Unlike hosting at a single Internet site, the InterVU Network employs an intelligent, globally distributed network that automatically delivers video content to viewers from the electronically closest site.
</BLOCKQUOTE>
</P>
</UL>
